        <h1 class="ph-title">The Art of <em>Rare Perfumery</em></h1>
        <p class="ph-sub">Beyond the everyday lies a world of rare ingredients, hand-finished bottles and houses that treat perfume as fine art. This is our most refined edit — the fragrances worth saving for, curated and 100% authentic.</p>
