    <!-- ABOUT-STYLE INTRO -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-split fade-up">
          <div class="about-figure"><img src="{{ 'cat-luxury.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="A luxury perfume bottle catching the light" /></div>
          <div class="about-body">
            <span class="label">What Makes It Luxury</span>
            <h2 class="sec-title">More Than a <em>Price Tag</em></h2>
            <p>True luxury in perfumery is not measured in dirhams alone. It is the natural jasmine picked at dawn, the frankincense sourced from a single region, the years a perfumer spends refining a single accord. It is quality you can smell — depth, longevity and a character that never feels mass-produced.</p>
            <p>A luxury fragrance rewards patience. It evolves on the skin for hours, revealing facets a cheaper composition never could. When you wear one, you are wearing craftsmanship — and that is exactly what this collection celebrates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THREE ASPECTS -->
    <section class="section alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="sec-head center fade-up">
          <span class="label">The Marks of Luxury</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title">Three Things That Set It <em>Apart</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-sub">What you are really paying for when you invest in a luxury fragrance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-grid fade-up">
          <div class="usp-card">
            <div class="usp-ic"><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">diamond</span></div>
            <h3>Rare Ingredients</h3>
            <p>Natural oud, ambergris, orris butter and precious florals — materials so costly and scarce they are measured by the gram. Their richness and nuance simply cannot be faked with synthetics alone.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="usp-card">
            <div class="usp-ic"><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">brush</span></div>
            <h3>Artisanal Craftsmanship</h3>
            <p>Small-batch maceration, hand-polished flacons and perfumers given the freedom to create without compromise. Every stage is deliberate, and every bottle reflects it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="usp-card">
            <div class="usp-ic"><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">workspace_premium</span></div>
            <h3>Exclusive Collaborations</h3>
            <p>Limited editions and house collaborations produce compositions you will rarely encounter elsewhere — the kind of scent that becomes a true, unmistakable signature.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
