            <h2>Amouage — The Gift of Kings</h2>
            <p>Born from a royal commission to revive the ancient art of Arabian perfumery, Amouage builds its fragrances around genuine Omani frankincense, rose and precious oud. Compositions like Interlude Man are famous for their intensity and remarkable longevity — a smoky, resinous statement that unfolds over an entire day and defines what modern Gulf luxury smells like.</p>
            <p>It is perfumery without shortcuts: rare materials, uncompromising concentration and a signature that lingers long after you have left the room.</p>
            <a class="btn-ghost" href="/collections/luxury">Explore the luxury collection <span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">arrow_forward</span></a>
