    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="faq" id="faq">
      <div class="faq-inner">
        <div class="faq-head fade-up">
          <span class="label">Luxury, Answered</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title">Questions Before You <em>Invest</em></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list fade-up">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-q">Are your luxury fragrances guaranteed authentic?<span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">add</span></summary>
            <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. Every fragrance we sell — from Lattafa to Amouage — is 100% authentic with fully verified sourcing. We stand behind each bottle, and our WhatsApp team, available 10am to 7pm, can confirm batch details before you order for complete peace of mind.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-q">Can I try a luxury scent before buying a full bottle?<span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">add</span></summary>
            <div class="faq-a">Yes. Discovery sets and travel-sized samples let you live with a fragrance for a few days before committing — the smartest way to invest in a premium scent. Ask our concierge for a curated sample kit built around your taste.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-q">How should I care for an expensive fragrance?<span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">add</span></summary>
            <div class="faq-a">Store it cool, dark and sealed — ideally in its original box, away from heat and sunlight. Proper storage keeps rare-ingredient compositions performing beautifully for years. Our <a href="/pages/care-storage">Care &amp; Storage guide</a> covers everything in detail.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-q">Do you offer payment plans on luxury purchases?<span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">add</span></summary>
            <div class="faq-a">Yes. Tabby and Tamara let you pay later, interest-free in instalments, and Cash on Delivery is available across all Emirates. Free delivery applies to every order above AED 150.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-q">What if the fragrance isn't right for me?<span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">add</span></summary>
            <div class="faq-a">We offer 7-day easy returns on unopened, sealed products — simply message our team on WhatsApp and we will arrange a collection. Trying a discovery set first is the best way to be sure before opening a full bottle.</div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
